Sentencas: Chromium deposition and poisoning of La2NiO4 cathode of solid oxide fuel cell were studied.
Titulo: Chromium deposition and poisoning of La2NiO4 cathode of solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: La2NiO4 cathode showed stable performance in the presence of metallic interconnects.
Titulo: Chromium deposition and poisoning of La2NiO4 cathode of solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Comparing with the polarization resistance (R-p) of La2NiO4 cathode in the absence of metallic interconnects, R-p, did not change in the presence of metallic interconnect.
Titulo: Chromium deposition and poisoning of La2NiO4 cathode of solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: After electrical conductivity relaxation method, La2NiO4 with high surface oxygen diffusion coefficients working under Cr atmosphere improved the oxygen reduction kinetics and increased cathode O-2 reduction reaction rates.
Titulo: Chromium deposition and poisoning of La2NiO4 cathode of solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: No chromium deposition was observed on the La2NiO4 cathode surface after polarization for 20 h at 800 degrees C.
Titulo: Chromium deposition and poisoning of La2NiO4 cathode of solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The chemical compatibility of La2NiO4/Cr2O3 and La2NiO4/Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 (GDC) study indicates that La2NiO4 did not react with Cr2O3 and GDC under the operating temperature.
Titulo: Chromium deposition and poisoning of La2NiO4 cathode of solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The results indicate that La(2)NiO(4 )cathode is a potential chromium-tolerant material of solid oxide fuel cell.
Titulo: Chromium deposition and poisoning of La2NiO4 cathode of solid oxide fuel cell
